<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>SI Unit Converter</title>
    <!-- โหลด Tailwind CSS -->
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <!-- โหลด Lucide Icons สำหรับ Vanilla JS -->
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/lucide@latest"></script>
    <style>
        /* Custom scrollbar styles */
        .custom-scrollbar::-webkit-scrollbar { height: 6px; width: 6px; }
        .custom-scrollbar::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background-color: #cbd5e1; border-radius: 3px; }
        .hidden { display: none !important; }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-50 text-slate-800 font-sans pb-12 min-h-screen">

    <!-- Header Section -->
    <header class="bg-blue-700 text-white shadow-md">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-6 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center justify-between gap-4">
                <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                    <i data-lucide="calculator" class="h-8 w-8 text-blue-200"></i>
                    <h1 id="ui-title-main" class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight">SI Unit Converter</h1>
                </div>
                
                <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
                    <!-- Language Toggle Switch -->
                    <div class="flex items-center bg-slate-100 p-1 rounded-lg shadow-inner">
                        <button id="lang-en" onclick="setLanguage('en')" class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-md font-bold text-sm transition-all duration-200 text-slate-500 hover:text-blue-600">
                            EN
                        </button>
                        <button id="lang-th" onclick="setLanguage('th')" class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-md font-bold text-sm transition-all duration-200 bg-white text-orange-500 shadow-sm">
                            TH
                        </button>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="hidden sm:flex items-center space-x-2 bg-blue-800 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full text-sm">
                        <i data-lucide="book-open" class="h-4 w-4"></i>
                        <span id="ui-tutorial-btn">Interactive Tutorial</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <p id="ui-subtitle-main" class="mt-3 text-blue-100 text-sm md:text-base">
                Learn how to convert various units into the International System of Units (SI).
            </p>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Main Content Area -->
    <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 mt-8">
        
        <!-- Detailed Educational Guide Section -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-blue-100 overflow-hidden mb-8">
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 lg:p-8">
                <div class="flex items-center space-x-3 mb-6">
                    <div class="bg-blue-600 text-white p-2 rounded-lg">
                        <i data-lucide="book-open" class="h-6 w-6"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h2 id="ui-guide-header" class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800">Learning Guide: Understanding SI Unit Conversion</h2>
                </div>
                
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                    <div class="bg-white p-5 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100/50 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
                        <div class="flex items-center space-x-2 mb-3">
                            <div class="bg-indigo-100 p-1.5 rounded text-indigo-700"><i data-lucide="info" class="h-5 w-5"></i></div>
                            <h3 id="ui-guide-1-title" class="font-semibold text-slate-800 text-lg">1. What is the SI System?</h3>
                        </div>
                        <p id="ui-guide-1-desc" class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                            The <strong>SI System (International System of Units)</strong> is the standard metric system used globally (e.g., meters, kilograms, seconds) to ensure consistency in science, engineering, and commerce.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="bg-white p-5 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100/50 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
                        <div class="flex items-center space-x-2 mb-3">
                            <div class="bg-emerald-100 p-1.5 rounded text-emerald-700"><i data-lucide="arrow-left-right" class="h-5 w-5"></i></div>
                            <h3 id="ui-guide-2-title" class="font-semibold text-slate-800 text-lg">2. Conversion Principles</h3>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                            <span id="ui-guide-2-desc-1">We use a <strong>"Conversion Factor"</strong> or a specific formula to convert units:</span>
                            <br/><br/>
                            <span class="text-emerald-700 font-medium" id="ui-guide-2-desc-2">➔ To SI: Follow the base formula (usually multiply by the factor).</span>
                            <br/>
                            <span class="text-blue-700 font-medium" id="ui-guide-2-desc-3">➔ From SI: Use the inverse operation (if the original formula multiplies, you divide).</span>
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="bg-white p-5 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100/50 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
                        <div class="flex items-center space-x-2 mb-3">
                            <div class="bg-amber-100 p-1.5 rounded text-amber-700"><i data-lucide="calculator" class="h-5 w-5"></i></div>
                            <h3 id="ui-guide-3-title" class="font-semibold text-slate-800 text-lg">3. Calculation Example</h3>
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed space-y-2">
                            <p id="ui-guide-3-desc">Suppose we know that <strong>1 foot = 0.3048 meters (SI)</strong></p>
                            <div class="bg-slate-50 p-2 rounded border border-slate-100 text-xs font-mono">
                                <span class="text-slate-500" id="ui-guide-3-ex1">Converting 10 feet ➔ m (Multiply)</span><br/>
                                10 × 0.3048 = 3.048 m
                            </div>
                            <div class="bg-slate-50 p-2 rounded border border-slate-100 text-xs font-mono">
                                <span class="text-slate-500" id="ui-guide-3-ex2">Converting 3.048 m ➔ feet (Divide)</span><br/>
                                3.048 ÷ 0.3048 = 10 feet
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="mt-6 bg-blue-100/50 p-3 rounded-lg flex items-start sm:items-center text-sm text-blue-800">
                    <i data-lucide="check-circle-2" class="h-5 w-5 mr-2 flex-shrink-0 text-blue-600"></i>
                    <p id="ui-how-to-use"><strong>How to use:</strong> Select a category on the left, enter a number, and choose your unit. The system will show step-by-step calculations below. Use the toggle button to switch conversion modes.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Mode Selection Toggle (Highly Visible before the calculator) -->
        <div class="bg-slate-200/60 p-2 rounded-2xl flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-2 mb-8 shadow-inner border border-slate-200">
            <button id="btn-mode-to-si" onclick="setMode('to-si')" class="w-full py-4 px-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-base sm:text-lg flex items-center justify-center transition-all duration-300 bg-blue-600 text-white shadow-md">
                <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="h-6 w-6 mr-2"></i>
                <span id="ui-tab-to-si">Mode 1: Non-SI ➔ SI</span>
            </button>
            <button id="btn-mode-from-si" onclick="setMode('from-si')" class="w-full py-4 px-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-base sm:text-lg flex items-center justify-center transition-all duration-300 bg-transparent text-slate-500 hover:bg-white hover:text-slate-800 hover:shadow-sm">
                <i data-lucide="arrow-left-right" class="h-6 w-6 mr-2"></i>
                <span id="ui-tab-from-si">Mode 2: SI ➔ Non-SI</span>
            </button>
        </div>

        <!-- Converter Controls Layout -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            
            <!-- Left Column: Category Controls -->
            <div class="md:col-span-1 space-y-6">
                <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200 p-5">
                    <label id="ui-step-1-title" class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 mb-3">
                        1. Select Quantity to Measure
                    </label>
                    <div id="category-list" class="space-y-2 max-h-96 overflow-y-auto pr-2 custom-scrollbar">
                        <!-- Category buttons will be injected here by JS -->
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- SI Unit Info for selected category -->
                <div class="bg-amber-50 rounded-xl border border-amber-200 p-4">
                    <div class="flex items-center space-x-2 text-amber-800 font-medium mb-1">
                        <i data-lucide="check-circle-2" class="h-4 w-4"></i>
                        <span id="ui-target-si-title">Target SI Unit</span>
                    </div>
                    <p id="si-info-text" class="text-amber-900 text-sm"></p>
                    <div id="si-info-symbol" class="mt-2 text-2xl font-bold text-amber-600 text-center py-2 bg-amber-100/50 rounded-lg"></div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Right Column: Interactive Converter & Results -->
            <div class="md:col-span-2 space-y-6">
                
                <!-- Input Form -->
                <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200 p-6">
                    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:justify-between sm:items-center mb-6 gap-3">
                        <h3 id="form-title" class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">
                            2. Enter Value to Convert
                        </h3>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 items-center">
                        <div class="w-full">
                            <label id="input-label" class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-600 mb-1">
                                Numeric Value (Initial Unit)
                            </label>
                            <div class="relative flex items-center">
                                <input
                                    id="input-value"
                                    type="number"
                                    value="1"
                                    class="w-full pl-4 pr-16 py-3 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-blue-500 outline-none transition-shadow text-lg font-medium"
                                    placeholder="e.g. 100"
                                />
                                <span id="input-unit-symbol" class="absolute right-4 text-slate-500 font-bold hidden"></span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="w-full">
                            <label id="select-label" class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-600 mb-1">
                                Initial Unit
                            </label>
                            <div class="relative group">
                                <select
                                    id="unit-select"
                                    class="w-full pl-4 pr-10 py-3 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-blue-500 outline-none appearance-none cursor-pointer text-lg hover:border-blue-400 transition-colors font-medium text-slate-700"
                                >
                                    <!-- Options injected via JS -->
                                </select>
                                <div class="absolute inset-y-0 right-0 flex items-center pr-3 pointer-events-none text-slate-400 group-hover:text-blue-500 transition-colors">
                                    <i data-lucide="chevron-down" class="h-5 w-5"></i>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <button
                        id="convert-btn"
                        onclick="handleConvert()"
                        class="mt-6 w-full font-bold py-4 px-4 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center space-x-2 transition-colors duration-200 text-white shadow-md bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-lg"
                    >
                        <span id="ui-btn-calc">Calculate Conversion</span>
                        <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="h-6 w-6"></i>
                    </button>
                </div>

                <!-- Results Display -->
                <div id="result-box" class="hidden bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md border border-emerald-200 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-500">
                    <div class="bg-emerald-50 px-6 py-4 border-b border-emerald-100 flex items-center justify-between">
                        <h3 id="ui-res-title" class="text-emerald-800 font-bold text-lg">Conversion Result</h3>
                        <button 
                            onclick="resetResult()"
                            class="text-emerald-600 hover:text-emerald-800 flex items-center text-sm font-medium bg-white/50 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg transition-colors hover:bg-white"
                        >
                            <i data-lucide="rotate-ccw" class="h-4 w-4 mr-1"></i> <span id="ui-res-reset">Reset</span>
                        </button>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="p-6">
                        <!-- Big Number Result -->
                        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-4 text-center md:text-left mb-8">
                            <div class="bg-slate-100 px-4 py-3 rounded-lg flex items-baseline border border-slate-200">
                                <span id="res-input-val" class="text-xl text-slate-700 font-medium">1</span>
                                <span id="res-input-unit" class="text-sm text-slate-500 ml-1">Unit</span>
                            </div>
                            
                            <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="h-6 w-6 text-slate-400"></i>
                            
                            <div class="bg-emerald-100 px-6 py-4 rounded-xl border border-emerald-300 shadow-inner flex items-baseline">
                                <span id="res-output-val" class="text-3xl font-bold text-emerald-800">Result</span>
                                <span id="res-output-unit" class="text-xl font-bold text-emerald-600 ml-2">SI</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Step by Step Explanation -->
                        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-lg p-5 border border-slate-200">
                            <h4 id="ui-step-logic-title" class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-700 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">
                                Step-by-Step Logic
                            </h4>
                            <div class="space-y-3 font-mono text-sm text-slate-800">
                                <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center gap-1 sm:gap-0">
                                    <span id="ui-lbl-factor" class="w-48 text-slate-500 flex-shrink-0 font-sans text-xs sm:text-sm font-medium">Conversion Factor:</span>
                                    <span id="step-factor" class="bg-emerald-50 px-2 py-1 rounded border border-emerald-200 text-emerald-700 font-bold"></span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center gap-1 sm:gap-0">
                                    <span id="ui-lbl-principle" class="w-48 text-slate-500 flex-shrink-0 font-sans text-xs sm:text-sm font-medium">Principle:</span>
                                    <span id="step-principle" class="bg-white px-2 py-1 rounded border border-slate-200 text-slate-600"></span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center gap-1 sm:gap-0">
                                    <span id="ui-lbl-formula" class="w-48 text-slate-500 flex-shrink-0 font-sans text-xs sm:text-sm font-medium">Formula:</span>
                                    <span id="step-formula" class="bg-white px-2 py-1 rounded border border-slate-200 font-medium"></span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center gap-1 sm:gap-0">
                                    <span id="ui-lbl-calc" class="w-48 text-slate-500 flex-shrink-0 font-sans text-xs sm:text-sm font-medium">Substitute & Calculate:</span>
                                    <span id="step-calc" class="bg-blue-50 px-2 py-1 rounded border border-blue-200 text-blue-700 font-bold"></span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center pt-4 border-t border-slate-200 mt-3 gap-1 sm:gap-0">
                                    <span id="ui-lbl-final" class="w-48 font-bold text-emerald-600 flex-shrink-0 font-sans text-sm">Final Result:</span>
                                    <span id="step-final" class="font-bold text-slate-900 text-base bg-emerald-100 px-3 py-1 rounded-md border border-emerald-300"></span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <!-- Footer & Credits -->
    <footer class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 mt-16 mb-8 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
        <div class="pt-8 border-t border-slate-200">
            <p id="ui-footer-dev" class="text-slate-500 text-sm">
                Developed with ❤️ by Gemini (Google AI) | Designed for learning
            </p>
            <div class="mt-2 text-slate-600 text-sm bg-slate-100 inline-block px-4 py-2 rounded-full shadow-sm">
                <span id="ui-footer-credit">Special Thanks & Credits to: </span>
                <a href="https://opensimlab.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="font-semibold text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 hover:underline transition-colors ml-1">
                    OpenSimLab.org
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

